Tonight while driving to Walmart because you know I needed the glue. Violet said “mommy will I have PANS the rest of my life?” For the first time in a long time I had to tell her I’m not sure. I had to tell her Autoimmune diseases are tricky but she’s getting the needed treatment and we will do everything to make it better. 18 months since our lives forever changed. #pansawareness #pandasawareness #pandaspans
